profile:
At Restoration 1 London we specialize in water damage restoration services. We also offer mould remediation, fire and smoke clean up and storm response services. We take care of cleaning up any water leak with our extraction service and state of the art drying systems.

We can help you to remove of all the water, dry your carpets, floors, walls and furniture to restore your home or office to its original condition or even better. We perform restoration services for both residential and commercial properties.

No job is too big or too small for us. Since we work with the insurance company, but not for the insurance company, our commitment is to you, the property owner and your needs. Restoration 1 will take complete care of you and guide you through the entire process of getting your property back to normal as quickly as possible.

* Water Damage Restoration * Sewage Cleanup * Flood Pump-out & Extraction * Mould Remediation * Fire & Smoke Cleanup * Leaking Basement * Wet Basement Repair * Storm Response

profile:
Promus London has been the top provider of London property damage restoration services for years. What makes us the very best at what we do is personal attention to the needs of every customer. We understand that dealing with damage to property is an extremely stressful experience and we want you to realize that our main objective is making this process as smooth as can be for you and your family. We approach every single property damage restoration project with an exceptional level of professionalism and compassion.

Our London Disaster Restoration Team is composed of highly trained professionals that are fully accessible to you from your first call to the final day of your restoration project. Needless to say, we’re also fully insured and licensed. To talk to one of our Property Damage Restoration Specialists call (226) 271-1133 and get your home or business back to normal.

Our Restoration experts will perform a complete analysis of your damage and provide an accurate no-obligation estimate. We make the restoration process headache-free for both the property owner and the insurance provider by billing the insurance company directly and helping the claim get processed quicker. Should your damages not be covered by your insurance provider, Promus London will still ensure that you get the best prices and service around. So call our Property Damage Restoration team now at (226) 271-1133 for 24/7 help.

profile:
A BIT ABOUT US
Experienced.  Certified.  Insured.  Trusted

From our experience to our methods used - we do things differently from any other mould removal company.  

We test for mould without tearing up your home.  If we find anyting, we perform mould removal using the most effective process. We then guarantee our work.  We have the most experienced mould remediation team.  We are quick, discreet and most of all, thorough.

With JohnstonPros we perform all of our Air Quality and Restoration Services. Our competitors subcontract out to the lowest bidder who happens to be on hand that day.  

We have the most highly skilled and capable team in South Western Ontario. We can handle any structural issues from the ground up -
 literally starting at the foundation, structural supports, and floor joists working our way up to attic insulation, ventilation, and shingling. 

When it comes to flood damage, removal of hazardous materials and removal of mould there is no better team to call than us. We are fully equipped to dry your home and safely remove any damaged material with dehumidifiers, fans, air scrubbers, negative air machines, and industrial vacuums all meeting EACO standards for safety. 

Even for the easy stuff we are fast polite and effective, We can remove, replace all the insulation in an attic and clean all the ducts in an average house in a single day. 

We handle small dry wall repairs to massive rebuilds, touch up painting to repainting an entire house from walls, ceilings, and trim.Installing lights and changing receptacles to tracing electrical shorts and replacing damaged wire. Changing a roof vent to re-shingling the entire roof. We even have some of the least invasive inspections techniques, with flexible wall scopes, moister meters, and stud finders. So we have no need to remove large amounts of dry wall to find the problem(s). In short we are the only team you need!
name: Johnston Pros    Mold Pro And Flood Pro
